            <title><![CDATA[[哆啦A梦害怕]#维生素真的不要随便补# 感冒补充维C，口腔溃疡补充维B，抗老补充维E……[裂开]维生素真的有必要补吗？[话筒]卫提醒，对于正常成人来说，一般不需...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哆啦A梦害怕]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/doraemon/dr_03haipa-32e9b53caf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E9%9A%8F%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E9%9A%8F%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#维生素真的不要随便补#</span></a> 感冒补充维C，口腔溃疡补充维B，抗老补充维E……<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>维生素真的有必要补吗？<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>卫提醒，对于正常成人来说，一般不需要额外补充维生素，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B9%B1%E5%90%83%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E6%82%A3%E7%99%8C%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B9%B1%E5%90%83%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E6%82%A3%E7%99%8C%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#乱吃维生素增加患癌风险#</span></a>，盲目补充维生素，或过量摄入维生素，反而还会引起严重的健康问题。👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（四川大学华西医院）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hna4opqdwrj20u01vidsk.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hna4opr0crj20u01vik43.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hna4oprm2tj20u01vc4c4.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hna4opt8taj20u024h7jw.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hna4opsx49j20u02537ht.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hna4optzsgj20u0253tql.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
